{"tid":1687141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如一齊戴朵花之簡易自製poppy pin","createTime":"2019-11-01T15:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T23:48:26.000Z","uid":99723,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"72af16c033b407ccaef3a0c2eaf2ad348f78bd96","tid":1687141,"uid":99723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:25:47.000Z","msg":"有巴打提出十一月一齊戴poppy 詳情可以睇呢個post: <br />\n<br />\n不如我哋戴返朵花吖？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675415</a><br />\n<br />\n但香港都唔易買 所以決定試吓自己整<br />\n材料好簡單 只需要紅、綠色摺紙同一粒pin<br />\n<br />\n首先喺紅色紙上畫兩個橢圓形 剪落嚟就係朵花啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94MDoPb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94MDoPb.png&h=e24ee5b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再畫塊葉 畫好又剪落嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1rjSHY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1rjSHY.png&h=e414435d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住將塊葉痴落朵花 再用你屋企揾到嘅pin吉落去 就搞掂啦 寫寫下諗到可以加黑色紙痴住粒pin 咁就更完整<br />\ntadaaaaa<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KC9p3QW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKC9p3QW.png&h=e8494508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(仲可以順便支持段校長)</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都一齊整啦 聽日一齊戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4835ee3e1dc6dda4bc78559c739b20725ef7ef","tid":1687141,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f76761c5d4b814785d96bd8371275b35d420c79","tid":1687141,"uid":99723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"Lest we forget. 一齊戴poppy!"},{"pid":"bee5f2a3b3001552bbe6313eafa2f337b03b362f","tid":1687141,"uid":99723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"就算唔戴聽日都要維園見呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{